snippet.title: OPEN ALPHA IS NOW LIVE! LET’S. SIPHER. NOW!
snippet.description:
#SiphersAssemble #playSIPHER #OpenAlpha

No more waiting. All doors are wide open. Now, you can enter the world of Sipheria and explore everything it has to offer.

During the Open Alpha, we eagerly await your feedback on bugs, issues, gameplay, and more. We hope to receive as much feedback as possible to make the game even better.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon and wishing you a joyful Sipher Odyssey experience!
ARISE!

DOWNLOAD NOW 📱

iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/sipher-odyssey/id6443806584

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.atherlabs.sipherodyssey.arpg
